'''Yot beans''' were a food crop grown on [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]] known for their flavor and nutritional value. They were used in various dishes to enhance flavor.

[[Griggen Sylo|Griggen]] and [[Tashna Sylo]] harvested yot beans to feed their children as well as to sell offworld.

